{"tid":1802913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【LIHKG User Script】LIHKG發帖範文插件","createTime":"2019-12-29T20:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T06:46:57.000Z","uid":23094,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"031e55237f9372a7ae5673130053bb751c322166","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:25:04.000Z","msg":"又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又寫咗個LIHKG User Script<br />\n今次係發帖範文插件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的係想方便大家儲存自己經常用嘅回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Atoq9nP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtoq9nP.png&h=bed3c21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安裝方法<br />\nChrome: <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Ftampermonkey%2Fdhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=7ef44dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo</a><br />\nFirefox: <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Ftampermonkey%2F&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=73a0b99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/</a><br />\nIE: Sor9ry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n安裝咗Tampermonkey之後開呢個網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/kitce/851ab3b1d045bd597ed75ce82b96cac8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgist.github.com%2Fkitce%2F851ab3b1d045bd597ed75ce82b96cac8&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=81282214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gist.github.com/kitce/851ab3b1d045bd597ed75ce82b96cac8</a><br />\n撳右邊個 &quot;Raw&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaUmHMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaUmHMA.png&h=453c2779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自動開咗個新頁面出嚟，撳 &quot;Install&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7oyyTk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7oyyTk.png&h=afc1680a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安裝完成<br />\n<br />\n重新載入已經開咗嘅LIHKG網頁就OK<br />\n<br />\n用法好簡單<br />\n首先輸入你想儲存嘅回覆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JabL9o1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJabL9o1.png&h=2ea85fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後撳【儲存】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkNSPo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkNSPo6.png&h=de91c185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀個靚名佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GojJV4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGojJV4b.png&h=864feb89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就可以喺左邊個清單揀返<br />\n撳【載入】Load個範文入去內文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3q60YiC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3q60YiC.png&h=595bff23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撳【預設】Set佢做預設範文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oG6TyQZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoG6TyQZ.png&h=aa7439c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會多咗粒星<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwNrTUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwNrTUo.png&h=b19eea86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁之後開Post或者回覆都會自動Load呢個範文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n如果喺其中一個LIHKG頁面儲存／刪除任何範文<br />\n喺其他同時開住嘅LIHKG頁面唔會自動更新<br />\n需要手動重新載入網頁先有效果<br />\n簡單啲講，所有記錄都會係最後一次修改時嘅記錄"},{"pid":"cc4e42962c1c6dd3e09efcd846d203ed5e39a149","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4EEUmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4EEUmt.jpg&h=81cffd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有人必須要由維園出發<br />\n<br />\n不遲到 不插隊<br />\n一月一 維園見</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"14cea7c1d2fed61bbf5f8d6ce678ca80c57e84f6","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4EEUmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4EEUmt.jpg&h=81cffd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有人必須要由維園出發<br />\n<br />\n不遲到 不插隊<br />\n一月一 維園見</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"5993213b114ca893152286c489f3db67af2db56f","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T20:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4EEUmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4EEUmt.jpg&h=81cffd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有人必須要由維園出發<br />\n<br />\n不遲到 不插隊<br />\n一月一 維園見</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm