n><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbf49c67ac78ad98eaec36b0f5f12eff993fe562","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一月一 維園見<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩點鐘</span> 準時到<br />\n銅鑼灣 天后 炮台山<br />\n梗有一個地方俾你去到維園</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不遲到</span></span><br />\n搣甩壞習慣，早瞓早起身<br />\n越早啲多人，越振奮人心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不插隊</span></span><br />\n所有人必須要由維園出發<br />\n切勿分散出發／分散隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不主動屌狗</span></span><br />\n成本高，效益低，零傷害<br />\n考慮自身及同行手足嘅安全<br />\n屌狗前三思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不留守陣地</span></span><br />\n認清行動目標<br />\n冇目標唔好守，目標完成就走<br />\n記住唔係留得越耐貢獻越大<br />\nBe water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不食花生</span></span><br />\n遇到私了／裝飾／裝修，唔好停低食花生<br />\n切忌停留，保持流動<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非 - 將手上嘅遮傳過去<br />\n勇武 - 了解情況自行決定行動，唔好受煽動<br />\n半和勇 - 落雨記住開遮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過咗半年，請相信勇武手足嘅行動準則<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不忘初衷<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n和勇不分 民獨不分</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4EEUmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4EEUmt.jpg&h=81cffd89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f22bd4ff4c1bce510a9c4ca731246e797f42845","tid":1802913,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一月一 維園見<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩點鐘</span> 準時到<br />\n銅鑼灣 天后 炮台山<br />\n梗有一個地方俾你去到維園</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不遲到</span></span><br />\n搣甩壞習慣，早瞓早起身<br />\n越早啲多人，越振奮人心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不插隊</span></span><br />\n所有人必須要由維園出發<br />\n切勿分散出發／分散隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不主動屌狗</span></span><br />\n成本高，效益低，零傷害<br />\n考慮自身及同行手足嘅安全<br />\n屌狗前三思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不留守陣地</span></span><br />\n認清行動目標<br />\n冇目標唔好守，目標完成就走<br />\n記住唔係留得越耐貢獻越大<br />\nBe water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不食花生</span></span><br />\n遇到私了／裝飾／裝修，唔好停低食花生<br />\n切忌停留，保持流動<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非 - 將手上嘅遮傳過去<br />\n勇武 - 了解情況自行決定行動，唔好受煽動<br />\n半和勇 - 落雨記住開遮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過咗半年，請相信勇武手足嘅行動準